title: Digital Realty Schedules Third Quarter 2015 Earnings Release and Conference Call
text:
Digital Realty Schedules Third Quarter 2015 Earnings Release and Conference Call [October 08, 2015] Tweet 
SAN FRANCISCO , Oct. 8, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- Digital Realty Trust, Inc. (NYSE: DLR), a leading global provider of data center and colocation solutions, announced today that it will release its financial results for the third quarter 2015 after the market closes on Thursday, October 29 , 2015. The company will host a conference call to discuss these results at 5:30 p.m. EDT / 2:30 p.m. PDT on Thursday, October 29 , 2015. 
To participate in the live call, investors are invited to dial +1 (888) 317-6003 (for domestic callers) or +1 (412) 317-6061 (for international callers) and reference the conference ID # 8772359 at least five minutes prior to start time. A live webcast of the call will be available via the Investors section of Digital Realty's website at http://investor.digitalrealty.com . 
Telephone and webcast replays will be available after the live call. The telephone replay may be accessed by diling +1 (877) 344-7529 (for domestic callers) or +1 (412) 317-0088 (for international callers) and using the conference ID# 10073885. The webcast replay may be accessed on Digital Realty's website one hour after the live call has concluded.
